V0709_01_00_00_0.text:
Turn on the ignition!
Full speed ahead!

V0709_01_00_01_0.text:
Revving the engines!
Let's roll, R6!

V0709_01_00_03_0.text:
I demand a Rush Duel!
I won't take no for an answer!

V0709_01_00_04_0.text: My Heavy Cavalry Style requires me to Duel fair and square!

V0709_01_00_05_0.text: Let's see how tough your monsters really are!

V0709_01_00_06_0.text: If you get in my way, I'm running you over!

V0709_01_00_07_0.text: Yuga, your Rush Duels are really fun.

V0709_01_00_08_0.text:
Tialina- I mean, Tiger!
I promise to give it my all!

V0709_01_00_09_0.text: You won't destroy Rush Duels on my watch!

V0709_01_00_10_0.text: Yuga is building a new future, and I won't let you crush it!

V0709_48_00_00_0.text: I'm ready to build a victory!

V0709_03_00_04_0.text:
You're pretty good.
But this Duel isn't over!

V0709_03_00_05_0.text: You'll pay for sending my monsters to the scrapyard!

V0709_05_00_00_0.text: I won't stop until my shift is complete!

V0709_07_09_01_0.text: My Set card is good to go!

V0709_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0709_16_00_00_0.text: You're just not up to code!

V0709_21_00_00_1.text:
What are you gonna do?
You have to at least try something.

V0709_21_00_01_0.text:
You managed to survive.
That's impressive!

V0709_21_00_03_0.text: I can't wait to see what you have in store.

V0709_21_00_04_0.text: No matter what you try, I'll stop it!

V0709_21_00_05_0.text: I know it's hard, but hang in there okay?

V0709_28_00_01_0.text: Only the Heavy Cavalry Duel Club can win so decisively!

V0709_28_00_02_0.text:
That was great!
I can't wait to Duel you again!

V0709_28_00_03_0.text: Your tactics can't even stop a toy truck!

V0709_28_00_04_0.text: The Heavy Cavalry Duel Club digs up another victory!

V0709_28_00_05_0.text: Yuga, only you can get me this excited to Duel!

V0709_28_00_06_0.text: Yuga, your Rush Duel never ceases to amaze me.

V0709_28_00_06_1.text: You should join my construction crew!

V0709_28_00_07_1.text: Her crazy brother's name is Lucidien, not Luke.

V0709_28_00_08_0.text:
I don't just Duel for myself.
I Duel for my whole crew!

V0709_28_00_09_0.text: That was so much fun, Tialina!

V0709_28_00_10_0.text: We need to forget the past to build a new future.

V0709_28_00_11_0.text: Your curveballs couldn't strike me out.

V0709_29_00_00_0.text: I never knew you could counterattack like that!

V0709_29_00_01_0.text: Your monsters were really tough - and amazing!

V0709_29_00_02_0.text:
Argh...
But the Heavy Cavalry still rides forever!

V0709_29_00_03_0.text:
I lose.
I'll back down for today.

V0709_29_00_04_0.text: Seems there are some cracks in my strategy.

V0709_29_00_05_0.text: I look forward to Dueling you again, Yuga.

V0709_33_00_00_0.text: My family's legacy will steamroll you!

V0709_33_00_02_0.text: The Heavy Cavalry Style has lasted for generations!

V0709_33_00_03_0.text: Listen to the roar of my engines!

V0709_30_00_01_0.text: I'm disappointed you don't have the heart to take a risk.

V0709_30_00_02_0.text:
You're taunting me?
That's a mistake.

V0709_34_00_00_0.text: Can you stop with your nonsense?

V0709_34_00_01_0.text:
This is what I wanted!
A fight between the best of the best!

V0709_34_00_02_0.text: The Heavy Cavalry Style is my family's legacy!

V0709_34_00_03_0.text: We combine the might of machinery with our elite intellect!

V0709_34_00_04_0.text: Our diggers and excavators form an unbeatable cavalry!

V0709_34_00_05_0.text: We strike harder than wrecking balls and bulldozers!

V0709_34_00_07_0.text:
Shh!
R6 has something to say!

V0709_34_00_08_0.text: Nothing sounds sweeter than the purr of R6's engine!

V0709_34_00_09_0.text: Isn't R6's carbon alloy-encased hydraulic pump beautiful?

V0709_34_00_11_0.text: R6 is asking why you're not saying hi to him.

V0709_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links
Start your engines!

V0709_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm Asana Mutsuba!
President of the Heavy Cavalry Duel Club!

V0709_35_00_01_0.text: My name is Asana - and my heavy machinery are my friends!

V0709_36_00_01_0.text: I'm proud to have you on my team!

V0709_36_00_03_0.text:
You're up!
Let's win this together!

V0709_36_00_04_0.text:
I'm not the type to make excuses.
This mess is my fault.

V0709_36_00_05_0.text: This is a tough task, but I know you can do it!

V0709_36_00_06_0.text: Show me a move that only you can do, Yuga!

Fusion!!!

V0709_08_00_05_0.text: Building a building is an art in itself!

Constructor Art - Buildestruction!

V0709_08_00_10_1.text: These majestic mountains will help my strategy!

V0709_08_00_12_0.text: I send all my monsters to the Graveyard to play Gold Rush!

I activate my Trap!
The Three Cavalteers!

V0709_08_00_13_1.text: They'll get me through any disaster!

V0709_08_00_14_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Shield Burial!

V0709_08_00_15_0.text:
This'll stop you!
I activate the Trap, Constructor Blockade!

V0709_08_00_16_0.text:

Constructor Blockade!

V0709_08_00_16_1.text: It makes your monsters useless - not worthy of repair!

Constructor Resurrection!

I activate Wyrm Excavator's effect!
Arcadia Quake!

I activate Wyrm Excavator's effect!
Arcadia Quake!

I tear down one card!
And then I draw!

V0709_09_00_04_0.text: Nothing can stop it once it gets up to speed!

Emerge!
Wyrm Excavator the Heavy Cavalry Draco!

There is no route ahead for you!
Nor is there any retreat!

V0709_37_00_02_0.text: Rise from the land to tower over the terrain!

V0709_13_00_02_0.text: Scratch the sky, Constructor Sky Wyrm Gantry Dragon!

V0709_37_00_03_0.text: This powerful primate tunnels through the terrain!

V0709_37_00_03_1.text: Combining the strength of both mammal and machine!

Shake 'em into submission!

V0709_37_00_04_0.text: Burst out and spread your wings!

Beast Drive Mega Elephant!
